ExchangeExp[g, {s1, s2, ...}] is equivalent to ExchangeExp[{g, g, g}, {s1, \
s2, ...}], the unitary gate governed by the isotropic exchange Hamiltonian \
with coupling constant g. ExchangeExp[{s1, s2, ...}] is equivalent to \
ExchangeExp[{1, 1, 1}, {s1, s2, ...}], the unitary gate governed by the \
isotropic exchange Hamiltonian with the unit coupling constant.", 
